title: Pete Davidson | Ted Cruz Attacks Big Bird; Giuliani Admits He Didn’t Verify Election Claims: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at Rudy Giuliani admitting in a deposition that he didn’t try to verify his insane voter fraud lies and Ted Cruz picking a fight with Big Bird.

Then, Pete Davidson talks about Taylor Swift coming to SNL and collaborating with Emily Ratajkowski in an ad campaign.
